description:
In the year of 20XX, United Nation Allied Army tries to overpower the Yamato Empire from the Fareast. Colonel Irving of the Allied Army captures a beautiful Yamato lieutenant named Yamamoto. The prisoner&rsquo;s interrogation quickly turns into a grueling torture, while his captor ends up succumbing to his lust for his mysterious prisoner&hellip;

